{"tid":944681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"虛擬幣官網皮已收 幣少隨時玩完","createTime":"2018-12-17T10:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T04:48:30.000Z","uid":66943,"like":308,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"9268529a4fd67be1b1ea3bbf5a4a23b98dd2a6ef","tid":944681,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHQbot3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHQbot3.jpg&h=f6041dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幣少涉嫌為宣傳撒錢被捕，因此「揚威國際」，從宣傳效果睇，幣少可謂大贏家；未必一定是他極力推介的filecash coin（FCC），而是他本人也真的出了名，這對「金主」來說（如果有的話），幣少的身價只會愈來愈值錢。<br />\n<br />\n其實幣少於此時大肆宣傳香港新幣，正好可以吸納從內地大力整治幣圈後逃出的購買力；幣少被捕後，觀其FCC討論群組內不斷有內地的新投資者加入，求教如何跟他搵食，更有死忠更揚言幣少手持2200 bitcoin，大家「等睇表演炒底」云云，就知道今次宣傳，似乎是利大於弊。幣少事後還揚言坊間有很多假新聞，自己即將約見不同國家的記者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n之不過，可能因為撒錢後太高調、玩太大，物極必反的道理，其虛擬幣操作終被放在鎂光燈之下，今日好友傳來一篇文章正正踢爆弊少食大茶飯，講到FCC疑遭大戶控制，只有69位holders，因弊少太出位，令水魚太早醒覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4CAQaR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4CAQaR.png&h=45a9be88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實不只該文章，於Telegram另一群組早已有高手踢爆騙局。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9tnhi2R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9tnhi2R.png&h=46acea1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以目前情況睇，弊少應該玩完，原因如下：</span><br />\n<br />\n1.幣價單日已大插過一半<br />\n2.filecash coin官網已死<br />\n3.FCC的顧問被質疑身份<br />\n4.傳媒一致歸邊協助警方偵查弊少，揭發弊少與倫敦金某董事有關連<br />\n5.FCC相關網站、公司均被揭是海外註冊<br />\n6.虛擬幣左手交右手的刷量技倆已公開<br />\n7.大公牛已停FCC交易，差在內地官方未開聲<br />\n8.其他虛擬貨幣玩家開始圍堵，水魚更動搖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nU9GLH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnU9GLH7.png&h=63f7fea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幣價已蒸發<br />\n<br />\n如今連官網都死埋，進一步打擊投資者信心。<br />\n其實香港，早就奉行「搵食行遠啲」原則，太高調真係會出事呀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/虛幣官網已死-幣少隨時玩完-070232058.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%99%9B%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%BB-%E5%B9%A3%E5%B0%91%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%8C-070232058.html&d=38KyZA03mmW%2Bd8urcvfUcf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7e559c49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/虛幣官網已死-幣少隨時玩完-070232058.html</a>"},{"pid":"aade93d18927cc8cd00ce6f5d584a8855c5efa85","tid":944681,"uid":7903,"like":286,"dislike":0,"score":286,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人信已經好奇蹟"},{"pid":"0719b97ae2c2bc19db1c265543acbf2849d180d4","tid":944681,"uid":52122,"like":27,"dislike":56,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"假設幣少呢鋪真係番到身 大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a20fb920b05d2f8a775e267ee36ce75a2005294","tid":944681,"uid":69484,"like":86,"dislike":71,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"話曬叫風光過 又後生 幾叻仔 <br />\n彈番上黎都唔出奇"},{"pid":"227b2723152881475dbfbd85929cb4c6c01f4de5","tid":944681,"uid":65530,"like":238,"dislike":19,"score":219,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a6bcbfda567e60eb3bbe1116e0bd7a632b30af5","tid":944681,"uid":60092,"like":133,"dislike":2,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"佢都錢已袋啦點會有事，佢班弊少軍就仆街了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7886f3d639f31f5e3ffc97e8101f7350c2537e","tid":944681,"uid":48334,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:46:52.000Z","msg":"又改個名到時咪又復活lo"},{"pid":"bb5f0c3de25f277668289d4467881db4a85335c1","tid":944681,"uid":186072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"玩完咪做下過街老鼠囉"},{"pid":"c889c44e1a8376e716c20fe2f28a2faca0a1f966","tid":944681,"uid":28765,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":1,